### Create session

POST /session

> {%
# Set-Cookie: sessionId=02d9953d8adde451899be54638820b8e  
%}


### Get chunks

GET /chunks
Cookie: sessionId=02d9953d8adde451899be54638820b8e
Content-Type: application/pdf


> {%
[
  {
    "id": "0ff0c836-529a-418f-8ffa-12538b5d5a55",
    "title": "Zasady dynamiki",
